snippet: Malaysia have asked that an Asian Cup qualifier against North Korea be moved to a neutral venue, as relations between the two countries worsen after North Korean leader Kim Jong Un's estranged half-brother was killed in Malaysia....

headline.main: Kremlin Says Seriously Worried About North Korea Missile Drills
headline.print_headline: Kremlin Says Seriously Worried About North Korea Missile Drills

lead_paragraph: Malaysia have asked that an Asian Cup qualifier against North Korea be moved to a neutral venue, as relations between the two countries worsen after North Korean leader Kim Jong Un's estranged half-brother was killed in Malaysia.
